of GPUs is bounded. Finally,\nall the previous algorithms for hybrid architectures have been experimented on\na large number of simulations built on actual libraries. These simulations\nassess the good practical behavior of the algorithms with respect to the\nstate-of-the-art solutions, whenever these exist, or baseline algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Nov 2017 07:09:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-20"}
